{"sn24.70:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 24.70 ","sn24.70:0.2":"3. Tatiyagamanavagga ","sn24.70:0.3":"Adukkhamasukhisutta ","sn24.70:1.1":"Savatthinidanam. ","sn24.70:1.2":"“Kismim nu kho, bhikkhave, sati, kim upadaya, kim abhinivissa evam ditthi uppajjati: ","sn24.70:1.3":"‘adukkhamasukhi atta hoti arogo param marana’”ti? ","sn24.70:1.4":"“Bhagavammulaka no, bhante, dhamma …pe…. ","sn24.70:2.1":"“Rupe kho, bhikkhave, sati, rupam upadaya, rupam abhinivissa evam ditthi uppajjati: ","sn24.70:2.2":"‘adukkhamasukhi atta hoti arogo param marana’”ti. ","sn24.70:2.3":"“Vedanaya sati …pe… ","sn24.70:2.4":"sannaya sati … ","sn24.70:2.5":"sankharesu sati … ","sn24.70:2.6":"vinnane sati, vinnanam upadaya, vinnanam abhinivissa evam ditthi uppajjati: ","sn24.70:2.7":"‘adukkhamasukhi atta hoti arogo param marana’ti. ","sn24.70:3.1":"Tam kim mannatha, bhikkhave, ","sn24.70:3.2":"rupam niccam va aniccam va”ti? ","sn24.70:3.3":"“Aniccam, bhante” …pe… viparinamadhammam, ","sn24.70:3.4":"api nu tam anupadaya evam ditthi uppajjeyya: ","sn24.70:3.5":"‘adukkhamasukhi atta hoti arogo param marana’”ti? ","sn24.70:3.6":"“No hetam, bhante”. ","sn24.70:3.7":"“Iti kho, bhikkhave, yadaniccam tam dukkham. ","sn24.70:3.8":"Tasmim sati, tadupadaya evam ditthi uppajjati: ","sn24.70:3.9":"‘adukkhamasukhi atta hoti arogo param marana’”ti. ","sn24.70:3.10":"“Vedana …pe… ","sn24.70:3.11":"sanna … ","sn24.70:3.12":"sankhara … ","sn24.70:3.13":"vinnanam niccam va aniccam va”ti? ","sn24.70:3.14":"“Aniccam, bhante” …pe… viparinamadhammam, ","sn24.70:3.15":"api nu tam anupadaya evam ditthi uppajjeyya: ","sn24.70:3.16":"‘adukkhamasukhi atta hoti arogo param marana’”ti? ","sn24.70:3.17":"“No hetam, bhante”. ","sn24.70:3.18":"“Iti kho, bhikkhave, yadaniccam tam dukkham. ","sn24.70:3.19":"Tasmim sati, tadupadaya evam ditthi uppajjati: ","sn24.70:3.20":"‘adukkhamasukhi atta hoti arogo param marana’”ti. ","sn24.70:3.21":"Chabbisatimam. ","sn24.70:3.22":"Tatiyapeyyalo. "}